com.datascience.hadoop

Class ListWritable<T extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.datascience.hadoop.ListWritable<T>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Iterable<T>, Collection<T>, List<T>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable

    public class ListWritable<T extends org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable>
extends Object
implements List<T>, org.apache.hadoop.io.Writable
    Hadoop writable for lists containing writable fields.

    This is a small Writable implementation intended for storing sorted lists of values. Internally, a T[] pool is used to store and recycle lists of values of the given type for efficiency.

    Author:
    Jordan Halterman
